{"tid":2123002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 火眼實驗室遭業主入稟解約","createTime":"2020-07-24T10:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T10:23:44.000Z","uid":66324,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6e42abaec26daf53462b97a32ed5b4007f1b1051","tid":2123002,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1216904441986296/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fphotos%2Fa.384058221937593%2F1216904441986296%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3cbb2d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1216904441986296/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n【火眼實驗室遭業主入稟解約】港府委聘兩間內地公司為本港提供病毒檢測，其中「華大基因」旗下的華昇診斷中心，在大埔太平工業園開設「火眼實驗室」，引起附近居民憂慮。業主昨入稟高等法院，要求法庭根據《失實陳述條例》撤銷租約，並下令華昇交出單位。據了解，昨天仍有醫療物資進出「火眼實驗室」。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，原告大埔綉花工藝有限公司，今年6月根據合約，將大埔汀角路太平工業園A座三層租給被告華昇診斷中心有限公司。原告以《失實陳述條例》要求法庭取消租約，並下令被告盡快將單位交吉和賠償。<br />\n<br />\n大埔區議員文念志表示，這兩天收集簽名時，不少居民擔心火眼實驗室的環境衛生問題。"},{"pid":"db6d18fcc11b58b10a938b53c6877eb93385baf0","tid":2123002,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:34:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dd3ad3847bc1f003faaee520784c0e5d0a9123e","tid":2123002,"uid":278298,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:49:34.000Z","msg":"業主怕上身，受制裁連累"},{"pid":"e12ca31d25d4e1629eb875915edb91986f762499","tid":2123002,"uid":346701,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"業主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052b3dbb74d8888afbc4e57fddfe1279ed33404b","tid":2123002,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"竟然無人睇"},{"pid":"eb02dab44b69e44c8f1113f50449a3f72e077e99","tid":2123002,"uid":94982,"like":0,"d